    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged; Monte Carlo UQ completed with 2000 samples characterizing output uncertainty in hemolysis index. Achieved levels documented against required levels for MRL 5. Package accepted for submission as credibility evidence record notwithstanding factor gaps, which are recorded for remediation planning. UQ results provide output uncertainty bounds sufficient for regulatory filing at this stage; sensitivity analysis extending input driver characterization is planned for the follow-on assessment cycle.",
